00:58:13,517 --> 00:58:15,309
Razmislite o tem.

939
00:58:15,683 --> 00:58:19,434
Torej, razumno razmislite, zakaj naj to naredi vtis na vas,

940
00:58:19,975 --> 00:58:22,517
